1)It is used to call the method directly using :: operator.
2)Use for calling existing methods.
3)Code reusability
4)Existing method logic
5)Must be same data type argument during method call.

##Four types
1)Static method ref: class::static method
2)Constructor: class::new
3)Instance red: class::instance-method
4)Reference to instance method from instance: objRef::instanceMethod